{"tid":2238301,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(90年代) 王晶: 我的電影並非為香港觀眾而拍, 《百變星君》是為大陸觀眾而拍","createTime":"2020-10-11T04:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T09:07:14.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"06e582921c4cd3dc3f88f04ad7537c841b3eae85","tid":2238301,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:42:12.000Z","msg":"有人貼左1995年《電影雙週刊》呢個王家衛王晶嘅相對論專訪.&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/803879953032830/permalink/3414582741962525/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F803879953032830%2Fpermalink%2F3414582741962525%2F&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=e120ca10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/803879953032830/permalink/3414582741962525/</a><br />\n<br />\n王晶係訪問中,&nbsp;講到明佢既電影並非以香港作為市場對象. 例如《百變星君》主要是為大陸觀眾而拍.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEz3AOt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEz3AOt.jpg&h=dc2121d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad146435ff868e2e4740d808b191d0c8400fe50b","tid":2238301,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"好多人將王晶作為香港文化模範,&nbsp;但佢既戲多數唔係為香港人而拍.&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>[FACE 352期 專訪]<br />\n<br />\n<strong>王晶 : 香港人大部分又塵又冇水，我啲戲不嬲唔係拍畀香港人睇</strong><br />\n<br />\n中港矛盾愈演愈烈，連演藝界北上拍戲、唱歌嗰班，都鬱啲被鬧：「滾去大陸搵人仔啦！」王晶最坦白，第一句就認：<br />\n<br />\n「係呀，我係搵人仔呀！順手擸埋你哋之嘛！你哋話咪話囉，我都賺夠囉！」<br />\n<br />\n「而家香港人，大部分都係沙漠英雄，又塵又冇水，仲要好 mean咁去睇笑片。你咁 mean，為數又少，我做咩要 serve你班咁認真嘅人，唔去 serve上邊十三億人啫？就算睇戲嗰班得五千萬人，都已經養得起成個電影業喇！<br />\n<br />\n唔係香港人唔算得啲咩，係做生意之嘛，邊個畀多啲錢咪邊個為主囉，<strong>我哋以前啲戲都係拍畀台灣人睇之嘛！全世界啲生意都唔係專為香港人而設</strong>，所有企業唯一係得 TVB一心一意拍嘢畀香港人睇。要鬧，你班友最唔應該鬧 TVB！你叻喇、巴閉喇，咪又係睇《來自星星的你》、《繼承者們》，咪一樣 foolish？有幾叻啫？咪又係因為靚仔？分別在於佢哋用多多錢、多多技術、同班好靚嘅仔去拍個 foolish story之嘛！ TVB對白三十年不變，係因為黎耀祥同麥長青講啫，換著張智霖講，你咪又係話好！」<br />\n</em>"},{"pid":"57e671266c3048f82597b1738254673906ecebb7","tid":2238301,"uid":136416,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"傻閪垃圾晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續食肥d食到肚滿腸肥就岩<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>［20號就截！］德國聯署逐步圖文教學 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2237513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2237513</a><br />\n有12人受緊苦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3b744ad4808ebdb973f7774a63d8952bac80e2b8","tid":2238301,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57e671266c3048f82597b1738254673906ecebb7","tid":2238301,"uid":136416,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"傻閪垃圾晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續食肥d食到肚滿腸肥就岩<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>［20號就截！］德國聯署逐步圖文教學 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2237513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2237513</a><br />\n有12人受緊苦</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95e8a9dc9c0ffeb305af76a1f6367960f830df8","tid":2238301,"uid":40267,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xaZWbrH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxaZWbrH.jpg&h=291b86fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05f73edb052992cc82f1f0f400109486dfedd07c","tid":2238301,"uid":9091,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"其實佢講得冇錯<br />\n因為佢係生意